Package me.hapyl.spigotutils.module.block.display

Class DisplayEntity

java.lang.Object
me.hapyl.spigotutils.module.block.display.DisplayEntity
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<org.bukkit.entity.Display>, IDisplay
public class DisplayEntity extends Object implements Iterable<org.bukkit.entity.Display>, IDisplay
Represents a display entity. An entity consists of a head (always present) and children.

    • getTeleportDuration

      public int getTeleportDuration()
      Description copied from interface: IDisplay
      Gets the teleport duration of this display.
      • 0 means that updates are applied immediately.
      • 1 means that the display entity will move from current position to the updated one over one tick.
      • Higher values spread the movement over multiple ticks.
      Specified by:
      getTeleportDuration in interface IDisplay
      Returns:
      teleport duration
